        <briefdescription>
<para>Disable all power rails associated with a specific profile. </para>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>Iterates through the list of rails defined for the given profile and instructs the Rail Controller to turn them OFF.</para>
<para><simplesect kind="note"><para>This is typically used when transitioning out of a state, or to shut down specific subsystems associated with a mode.</para>
</simplesect>
<parameterlist kind="param"><parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
